article_title: Netanyahu orders military to plan Rafah evacuation
sentence: Reported  Israeli  air  strikes  on  Gaza  on  Friday  killed  at  least  15  people  including  eight  in  Rafah,  officials  from  the  Hamas-run  health  ministry  said.

article_title: Netanyahu orders military to plan Rafah evacuation
sentence: More  than  1,200  people  were  killed  during  the  Hamas  attacks  on  southern  Israel  on  7  October,  according  to  Israeli  officials.
